<P>
   Editors: The following items from The N.Y. Times Week in Review
for Sunday, Jan. 16, moved Saturday.
</P>
<P>
   On the dress page:
</P>
<P>
   INDIA-PAKISTAN-REVIEW (Undated) _ Relations between India and
Pakistan are at their worst in decades. Things weren't supposed to
